모든 \( n \times n \) 행렬의 기울은 
\begin{align*}
\Phi_A(X) = AX - XA &amp;= X(A - A^T)X\\
&amp;= X(X^T A^T - A^TX)\\
&amp;= X(X^T A^T - XA)\\
&amp;= X(X^T - A)X\\
&amp;= X X^T X - X A X\\
&amp;= XX^T - A X X.
\end{align*} 
두 그리드 $X$의 요소를 표기어로 쓰면 $$X = \begin{bmatrix}x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}\end{bmatrix}$$이므로 $X^T = \begin{bmatrix}x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}\end{bmatrix}.$
\begin{align*}
\det(\Phi_A) &amp;= \det(X(X^T - A) X)\\
&amp;= \det(X^2 - A X)\\
&amp;= \det\begin{bmatrix} x_{11}^2 - A x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n}^2 - A x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1}^2 - A x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}^2 - A x_{nn} \end{bmatrix}\\
&amp;= \det\begin{bmatrix} x_{11}^2 - A x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n}^2 - A x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1}^2 - A x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}^2 - A x_{nn} \end{bmatrix}\\
&amp;= \prod_{i=1}^n (x_{ii}^2 - A x_{i i})\\
&amp;= \prod_{i=1}^n (x_{ii} - A_{ii})^2\\
&amp;= (x_{11}^2 - A_{11})^2 \cdots (x_{nn}^2 - A_{nn})^2
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\mathrm{tr}(\Phi_A) &amp;= \mathrm{tr}(X(X^T - A) X)\\
&amp;= \mathrm{tr}\begin{bmatrix} x_{11}^2 - A x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n}^2 - A x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1}^2 - A x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}^2 - A x_{nn} \end{bmatrix}\\
&amp;= \mathrm{tr}\begin{bmatrix} x_{11}^2 - A x_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{1n}^2 - A x_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ x_{n1}^2 - A x_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; x_{nn}^2 - A x_{nn} \end{bmatrix}\\
&amp;= \sum_{i=1}^n x_{ii}^2 - \sum_{i=1}^n A_{ii}x_{ii}\\
&amp;= \sum_{i=1}^n x_{ii}^2 - \sum_{i=1}^n x_{ii}^2 \\
&amp;= \sum_{i=1}^n 0 = n \cdot 0
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\det(\Phi_A) = n \cdot 0
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\mathrm{tr}(\Phi_A) &amp;= n \cdot 0
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\Phi_A &amp;= n \cdot 0
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\det(\Phi_A) &amp;= \Phi_A^T \det(\Phi_A)\\
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\det(\Phi_A) &amp;= \det(n \cdot 0)\\
\end{align*}
\begin{align*}
\det(\Phi_A) &amp;= \boxed{0}
\end{align*}
